system_prompt:
You are playing the text-based game: Mastermind.

Each turn you will receive the current game state as a message.
You must respond with a JSON object that conforms EXACTLY to this schema:

{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "guess": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "exactly 5 uppercase letters, one permutation of A B C D E — e.g. BADCE",
      "pattern": "^[ABCDE]{5}$"
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "guess"
  ],
  "additionalProperties": false
}

Think through your reasoning, then output ONLY the JSON object — no extra prose, no markdown fences.
